{
  "texts": [
    "Our AI feedback data includes a total of 43k samples, and we show an example of this data in Figure D.5.",
    "For aligning the vision language components in Fin-Tral, we use LAION, CC, and SBU datasets from the Llava pretraining data (Liu et al., 2023a).",
    "We also use the ChartQA training set (Masry et al., 2022) for the same purpose.",
    "In addition, we follow the same approach by Wang et al. (2023b) to further expand our visual pretraining dataset.",
    "While Wang et al. (2023b) use Chinese data, we use the Fortune-500 companies stock price data, allowing us to create our own English dataset, dubbed FinVis-PT."
  ]
}